import {
  SignPanelContainer,
  SignPanelLogo,
  Panel,
  PanelInnerWrap,
  SignPanelTitleLogo,
  SignPanelTitle,
  SignPanelTitleDesc,
  SignPanelButton,
  SignPanelInput,
  LinkGroups,
  SignPanelChange,
  CancelButton
} from './SignPanelElements.js'

const SignPanel = ({ toggleSignPanel }) => {
  return (
      <SignPanelContainer>
        <Panel>
          <CancelButton onClick={toggleSignPanel} />
          <SignPanelLogo>Indielog</SignPanelLogo>
          <PanelInnerWrap>
            <SignPanelTitle>註冊</SignPanelTitle>
            <SignPanelTitleDesc>帳號</SignPanelTitleDesc>
            <SignPanelInput></SignPanelInput>
            <SignPanelTitleDesc>密碼</SignPanelTitleDesc>
            <SignPanelInput></SignPanelInput>
            <SignPanelTitleDesc>確認密碼</SignPanelTitleDesc>
            <SignPanelInput></SignPanelInput>
            <SignPanelButton>送出</SignPanelButton>
            <LinkGroups>
              <SignPanelChange>登入</SignPanelChange>
            </LinkGroups>
          </PanelInnerWrap>
        </Panel>
      </SignPanelContainer>
  )
}

export default SignPanel
